  "title": "Post-divorce custody arrangements and binuclear family structures of Flemish adolescents",
  "abstract": "Because of the tendency towards equal parental rights in post-divorce custody decisions, the number of children living partially in two households after divorce has increased. Because of this evolution, traditional family typologies have been challenged.",
